  <title>Listen to my music</title>

  <p>You can listen to songs with the Music app, which is located on your
  desktop. Click on the icon once to open it.</p>

  <p>When the music app loads, you will see some songs that already come with
  your computer. You can add as many songs as you like, from your own collection
  on another device, or by downloading more from the internet.</p>

  <list>
    <item>
      <p>Double click on a song to play it.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Pause the song by clicking the pause button on the top left hand
      corner.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Skip a song or go back to it by clicking on the left and right
      arrows.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click on the rectangle button to repeat the song or the whole
      track.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Click on the mixed arrows next to the rectangle to shuffle the songs.
      Click it again to play the songs in order.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Control the volume bar on the right. You can slide the round button to
      get to your desired volume. </p>
    </item>
  </list>
